work.work-title: Dear Lord and Father of mankind

encoding.software: PDFtoMusic Pro v1.6.5 Build 1B9E7 (c) Myriad - http://www.myriad-online.com

credit.credit-words: In simple trust like theirs who heard, Beside the Syrian sea, The gracious calling of the Lord, Let us, like them, without a word, Rise up and follow Thee.
O Sabbath rest by Galilee, O calm of hills above, Where Jesus knelt to share with Thee The silence of eternity, Interpreted by love!
Dear Lord and Father of mankind
Drop Thy still dews of quietness, Till all our strivings cease; Take from our souls the strain and stress, And let our ordered lives confess The beauty of Thy peace.
